No reason to call into question the transparent process at @BOENYC or integrity of workers at the polls. Baseless allegations undermine the democratic process. All valid votes should be counted & I will respect the results. I ask others to do the same. #QueensDA #CountEveryVote

As I said last week on election night #EveryVoteCounts and every vote must be counted. The people of Queens deserve no less. Congratulations to @MelindaKatz on her lead now that all the votes are in. #QueensDA
